Speaker 2: 25.

Speaker 2: Okay, perfect. All right.

Speaker 1: Okay, perfect.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 1: All right, perfect. That went through, so they'll be shipping out to you today.

Speaker 2: Okay, thank you so much.

Speaker 1: No problem. Have a great day.

Speaker 2: You too. Bye-bye.
